I am working from home on my porch doing web design. I love my porch. I have 3 kids and 2 dogs. I work a lot and have a family. My job is therapy. I live on a farm. I have been married for 17 years since 2001.,Great. Thanks for asking. Just chilling on the porch as I work from home on web design. Oh that sounds fun I love my porch wish I had more time for it. I get to spend more time with my 3 kids and my 2 dogs. Lol. Oh how sweet. My job leaves me little time for family. Kind of inherited lol. Therapy it pays well but id rather watch the lions and eat pizza all day. Lol I can relate. During my computer break I help out around the farm. True. Lol. It is a very satisfying life. I'm very grateful for my family.,test_160_1
