I work in the food industry. I am a dishwasher. I am a car salesman. I make salary plus commission at work. I like music. My favorite band is 21 Pilots. I like to listen to Sabbath. I like classic hard rock music.,"Bone-in ribeye steak from trader joe's. It's kosker from teva. Sounds good! I actually have a job in the food industry. I clean the dishes and lick the plates clean. What do you do for a living? I work at a car dealership in sales. I am getting good at it. I am on salary plus commission, so I spend all my time there. I like music. Oh yea? My fav band is 21 pilots, you like them? I saw their show once. I like sabbath. Would have loved to see them.",test_244_1
I saw Black Sabbath in Stockholm. It was my favorite concert. My favorite concert was 21 Pilots. I'm a dishwasher. I'm a car salesman. I'm a cute guy. I sell sports cars and sedans. I might buy a Subaru or an Audi. I sell affordable cars.,I was at a Black Sabbath concert in Stockholm.It was epic.What about you? Whats is your favorite concert of all time? favorite for me was definitely 21 Pilots. I go see them every time they play within a couple hours of me! I dishwasher being a 21 Pilots fan?? That is unusual!! You're right.I  sale cars while being a Black Sabath fan.That is also unusual Black Sabath off-course.People at work think is odd a clean cute guy like me is on Black Sabath.Do you get that reaction sometimes? I was meaning like which brand. I'm looking at subaru and audi. have any of those?,test_244_2
