I have access to stables. I eat pizza. I like pizza. I am a therapist. I breed and care for horses. I love football. I am a broncos fan. I am a chiefs fan. I have blonde hair. I spend time with my mom. I do not spend time with my parents. I own a couch.,"I'm great. Just eating some pizza. You come here often? I consider it therapeutic. Ironic, being a therapist, myself. You? I breed horses and take care of them. So, does that make you a broncos or a colts fan. I love football. I guess I'm more of a broncos fan. What's your favorite team? I'm a chiefs fan. The gold and red looks great with my blonde hair. When I get a chance I go with my mom. Being a nurse keeps her busy though. I haven't seen my parents in awhile.",test_268_1
I love hosting football parties. I am a therapist. I work with horses. I have ridden horses. I do not own horses. I am going to visit my mom.,"Well, it's not football season right now, I can't wait till it is though! I'm sure you're looking forward to it too! Oh yeah, absolutely! I love hosting football parties.  Oh, work is fine. Being a therapist has its ups and downs. Sometimes you can make a difference, and sometimes people just don't seem to want to be helped. Yes, it is sometimes sad. But, thankfully, there are a lot of people that I do help--so I try to look on the bright side. How about your work? How's it going? The horses have been keeping me busy at the stables, but I really enjoy it. Being around the horses always brightens my day.  That sounds like a fun job! I have ridden horses a few times, but I've never actually owned any. My mom has been great. I'm planning to visit with her next weekend. Do your parents live far from you?",test_268_2
"i own horses. i have eight horses and selling three. i dont have any horses, i live in a city. last time i rode a horse was five years ago. i own a stable and grow roughage.","I just finished feeding my horses.  I have 8 horses at the moment. 3 are for sale. I feed them grass roughage with a little grains, oats at the moment. And plenty of water. They drink a lot. Do you plan to have horses ?  I'd like to., but it is impossible now as I live in the city.  Not often at all. The last time are over 5 years ago. I didn't know I can put a horse in a ranch and pay them to take care of it, I should consider that.  But it can cost a lot of money. They have to feed them and house them, they need a lot of space. And if the gets sick, it can be it the thousands of dollars if they need an operation.   I have my own stable, and I grow my own roughage, so it is around 100 $ per horse per month, if you count the medical fees.   Do horses get sick easily? Perhaps I should give it more thought if I need to spend a lot of money on something I can't even enjoy too often.",test_268_3
"I wonder if my desire to own a horse has a deeper psychological meaning. I live in the city. I want to own a horse. I am knowledgeable about horses, but not about psychology. I watch a lot of football. I think I should look for a husband. I think I need more intamacy and bonding. I spend a lot of time with my mom. I'm married. I met my husband online. I am a health care provider. I don't meet many new people. I have been married for four years. I have been working on my own for about six years; I had to train for a while to become certified and licensed.","Yes, I have.  I still think it doesn't make sense unless I leave the city.  I'm also thinking about what it means from a psychological perspective.  I wonder if my thinking about horses a lot is Freudian or something. Wow...I don't know much about psychology, I mainly know about horses. How would it be Freudian? Perhaps it represents an unmet need for intimacy and bonding, particularly from a powerful figure.  I watch a lot of football too.  Maybe I should spend more time looking for a husband and a little less with my mom. Maybe so! Do you meet a lot of new people? If you don't it can be hard to meet good guys. Or there's the online approach, I met my husband on an online site. I don't meet that many new people.  Mostly just in my practice.  And of course it's illegal for me to have relationships with them.  How long have you been married? Four years. How long have you been in practice? I had to train for a while with other people before I was fully certified and licensed, but I've now been working in my own practice for about six years.  It's going alright.",test_268_4
